<p data-start=3D"638" data-end=3D"677">=E2=9C=94 Because <code data-start=
=3D"648" data-end=3D"651">+</code> operator is overloaded:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"678" data-end=3D"750">
<li data-start=3D"678" data-end=3D"712">
<p data-start=3D"680" data-end=3D"712">It does <em data-start=3D"688" data-=
